name: ServiceCloudVoice_Template
description:
This flow represents a sophisticated integration between Webex Contact Center and Salesforce Service Cloud Voice, enabling seamless voice call handling with intelligent routing and comprehensive event management.
- Salesforce Service Cloud Voice: Primary integration for voice call management
- Webex Contact Center: Platform handling the actual call flow, routing, variable passing, and (optional) AI Agent integration.

variables.description: Selected Agent by SCV Omni Flow

variables.name: SCV_VendorCallKey
variables.description: Unique Id for the call, used as reference to create the Voice Call Record

variables.description: Voice Call record Id and Vendor Call Key for the SCV Connector
